{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2997674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你需要挂靠一个社团/学院等，征得其同意，然后在学生清华走“大型活动审批”。以院系为例，需要经过院系团委、党委，校团委等，搭建舞台、拉电还需要保卫处、绿办、学生公寓办、电管科等。如果要进行宣传，宣传品也需要院校两级审批。然后演唱会当天把声音调小一点，以免紫8等宿舍楼抗议，再将dz挂上树洞。", "timestamp": 1637466966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997715, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": 2997674, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如果只是个人的 小小的那种呢", "timestamp": 1637467255, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997863, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": 2997715, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 紫操属于校管室外场地，任何活动均需要经过上述流程。", "timestamp": 1637468308, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": 2997715, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然 如果球宝大力支持，那这些就都不用", "timestamp": 1637468346, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997876, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": 2997715, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 或者Alice不说是演唱会 只是自己带着音响到紫操唱歌 声音小点 应该不会有人管。参考中秋夜紫操有很多演奏乐器的同学。", "timestamp": 1637468442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2997930, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 567869, "reply_to": 2997876, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 好滴好滴 明白啦 谢谢Alice！", "timestamp": 1637468798, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 567869, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "诚心想问一下 怎么能在紫草办演唱会呢（不是开玩笑", "timestamp": 1637466636, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637468797, "url": "", "vote": {}}}